		================================
		rfsctl - RedirFS Control Utility
			     README
		================================

This software is distributed under the Boost Software License, Version 1.0.

1. Introduction

	RedirFS Control Utility allows to manage filters registered to RedirFS
	from command line. This is preferred way how to manage filters, but the
	RedirFS sysfs interface can be used directly also.

	For an overview of the RedirFS project, visit 

		http://www.redirfs.org

2. Installation

	See the INSTALL file.

3. Documentation

	http://www.redirfs.org/tiki-index.php?page=redirfs_doc

4. Problems & Bugs
	
	http://www.redirfs.org/cgi-bin/bugzilla/index.cgi
